descriptionHtml:
[font=Verdana][b][u][size=4]Description[/size][/u][/b]
[size=3]Kalein lost her mother and father when she was very young. Being adopted into a loving family she learned how to fish and hunt. She has now set out on her path to find a greater calling in life and to discover the mysteries of the world.[/size]
[img]http://i66.tinypic.com/15xvfqh.jpg[/img]
[size=2]"Kalein Eldor, that is my name. My parents were murdered when I was eight and since then I have devoted my life to finding out why they were killed and stop anyone from suffering the same fate. I hunt monsters, I’ve hunted things from The Great Artoa to a Phylacine from the planes of Heera. All these creatures terrorise communities of people I take up contracts helping deliver people from these monstrosities, it’s not always easy and sometimes I really don’t want to kill them. I’m a nomad, I don’t have a place to call home anymore. I was given a home by a lovely family that fed me and kept me safe until I was ready to move out into the world by myself."

[/size][/font][size=4][u][b]Required files
